    "markdown": "### 18. Baidu ERNIE/Qianfan (China) — LLM ✓ TTS ⚠️ STT ⚠️\n\n**Status:** Active but **poor international access**. Registration often requires Chinese phone.\n\n`ernie-4.5` ($0.55/$2.20), `ernie-x1` ($0.28/$1.10). ERNIE 5.0 announced but public API status unclear. Legacy TTS/STT available but Chinese-focused. Proprietary API (not OpenAI-compatible). **Not recommended** for international BYOK app.",
